<subSubSection pageId="83" pageNumber="362" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="83.[786,1381,2386,2805]" lastBlockId="83.[175,1383,2812,3473]" pageId="83" pageNumber="362">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Goldman" authorityYear="1904" box="[789,975,2496,2529]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="83" pageNumber="362" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="picta">Neotoma picta</taxonomicName>
was described in 1904 but was later considered a subspecies of N. ferruginea. Subsequently, N. 
<taxonomicName box="[1168,1303,2575,2608]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="83" pageNumber="362" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ferruginea">ferruginea</taxonomicName>
containing subspecific N. 
<taxonomicName box="[1094,1186,2618,2647]" form="picta" pageId="83" pageNumber="362" rank="form">f. picta</taxonomicName>
was placed in N. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Baird" authorityYear="1855" box="[836,955,2653,2686]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="83" pageNumber="362" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="mexicana">mexicana</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Goldman" authorityYear="1904" box="[976,1160,2653,2686]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="83" pageNumber="362" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="picta">Neotoma picta</taxonomicName>
was reelevated to specific status based on genetic data. A revision is needed to determine if other subspecies currently included in N. mexicana should be assigned to N. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Goldman" authorityYear="1904" box="[597,661,2812,2845]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="83" pageNumber="362" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="picta">picta</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
