<subSubSection pageId="83" pageNumber="362" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="83.[1447,2653,287,484]" pageId="83" pageNumber="362">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1448,1796,330,359]" pageId="83" pageNumber="362">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. There are no known conservation risks facing the Painted Woodrat. Nevertheless, given its endemic status and relatively small distribution, an updated conservation assessment is needed.
</paragraph>
